The People of the State of Illinois ex rel. Leopold Sachs, appellee, v. William E. Dever et al., appellants.Gen. No. 30,126.

O’Connor, J., dissents.

Opinion filed January 20, 1926.Francis X. Busch, Corporation Counsel, for appellants; Albert H. Veeder and Joseph J. Thompson, Assistant Corporation Counsel, of counsel.James M. Burke, for appellee; Snyder & Cohn, of counsel. Mr. Presiding Justice Thomson

delivered the opinion of the court.
